  "title": "Lorry Crane Driver",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>•\tOperate a lorry crane for the lifting and delivery of goods to designated locations.</p>\n<p>•\tEnsure the safe loading and unloading of goods from the lorry.</p>\n<p>•\tPerform routine maintenance and upkeep of the lorry, and coordinate vehicle repairs and inspections as </p>\n<p>        needed.</p>\n<p>•\tUtilize navigation apps to find optimal routes and maintain familiarity with various routes.</p>\n<p>•\tAdhere to safety regulations and guidelines.</p>\n<p>•\tHandle any additional tasks as assigned.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>•\tPossess valid Singapore Class 4 Driving License</p>\n<p>•\tRequired to pass WSQ Lorry Crane Operator Certificate</p>\n<p>•\tOn the job training available</p>\n<p>•\t2 Years of Relevant Experience Preferred</p>\n<p>•\tAble to work independently</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Why Join Us?</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>At Ban Soon Huat Transport Trading, you’ll be part of a supportive and innovative environment that encourages professional growth and development. We offer a competitive salary with high basic salary package with additional incentives, comprehensive benefits, and a dynamic work culture where you can truly make a difference.</p>\n<p>You may drive home your lorry to park at your nearest URA Heavy Vehicle Carpark (subject to lot availability at these carparks: Ubi, Hougang, Loyang, Yishun, Joo Koon, Bt Batok, Tuas, Yio Chu Kang).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>WhatsApp 8660 4431 to arrange for interview or email your resume to bansoonhuat4@outlook.com</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
